# LS Colors Test
# Tests file listing with colors for different file types
Output examples/svgs/ls-colors.svg

Set Theme github-dark
Set Template macos
Set Title "Colored File Listing"
Set FontSize 14

Type "ls -la --color=always"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 1.5s

Type "ls -la --color=always src/"
Sleep 500ms
Enter
Sleep 2s
